Some of you guys may of seen this release on R-S, this is the third version i didnt post any of the previous versions on here. In this release i have started working on security stronghold but its incomplete, i Havent worked much on source so you will need to change alot of animation ID's, i might try fixing the bugs that i have included in the bugs list and re release it on the same thread.

Note: I have Cache packed nearly everything, so the cache is reasonably clean.

Features:

- Cache packed 660 items (with Examined all working but only 653 item models added)
- Cache packed 602 npc's
